Lewis opens up about overcoming a traumatic childhood, learning disabilities, and years of insecurity that shaped his path to personal growth. In this A Bit of Optimism episode, they dive into the insecurities we all carry, examine their relationship with money trauma, and reveal why courage is the gateway to genuinely liking who you are.
